data.title: Patrick Boyle, 10th Earl of Glasgow
data.meta_description: Patrick Robin Archibald Boyle, 10th Earl of Glasgow,, is a Scottish peer, politician and the current chief of Clan Boyle. The family seat is Kelburn Castle in Ayrshire. He currently sits as a Liberal Democrat peer in the House of Lords.
